What you need to know:

Mr Wanjigi was in Bondo as a chief guest at the fundraiser in aid of the St Michaels and All Angels Cathedral to put up synod plaza.So connected is Mr Wanjigi that he has openly claimed that he brokered the deal between Uhuru Kenyatta and William Ruto in his Muthaiga house, and that were it not for him, the Jubilee Alliance would not have been born.